'''Sandsurfing''' was a sport created by [[Laze Loneozner/Legends|Laze "Fixer" Loneozner]]. He invented it after consistently losing at other sports. Sandsurfing involved standing on two [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsor]] disks and being pulled by a [[Skiff/Legends|skiff]].

